                                <Span Text="Your comprehensive companion for exploring Formula One telemetry data. "/>
                                <Span Text="Dive deep into lap times, sector analysis, speed traces, and driver performance metrics from real F1 sessions." FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                            </FormattedString>
